author: roddey
msg: Added a couple of new files, to make some compilers happy. Moved

author: roddey
msg: Some compilers just can't handle a template class hidden away inside
the Cpp file that uses it. They must have them in split hpp/c files. So I
had to move a couple of small template classes out to their own file.
